author: Ildefonso Ortiz
title: Coronavirus Rises to 1,890 Confirmed Cases in Mexico
description: Mexican health officials revealed that the worst is yet to come as the number of cases of the novel coronavirus (COVID-19) continues to grow. The number climbed again on Saturday, reaching a total of 1,890 cases.
